Comment: 1,0:00:44.48,0:00:44.98,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Hey
Dialogue: 1,0:00:44.98,0:00:47.11,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,开端便是一切都顺序错乱
Dialogue: 1,0:00:47.11,0:00:49.99,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,一成不变的生活地覆天翻
Dialogue: 1,0:00:49.99,0:00:52.87,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,很久很久很久以前
Dialogue: 1,0:00:52.87,0:00:55.74,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,人还知吃吃喝喝舞中作乐
Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.74,0:00:58.41,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,今辛酸痛苦无止境  社会压力超负荷
Dialogue: 1,0:00:58.41,0:01:01.25,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,早间新闻将这常态播放着
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.25,0:01:02.96,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,逼着我睁开双眼  漱口洗脸
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.96,0:01:05.71,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,早餐一个汉堡打发  能不能来点奇迹使天地异变
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.71,0:01:07.05,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,做什么梦呢我傻吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.05,0:01:08.42,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Song of the dead
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.42,0:01:09.51,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Song of the dead
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.51,0:01:10.09,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,I wanna!!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.09,0:01:11.43,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Dancing, dancing
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.43,0:01:12.93,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Rolling, rolling
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.93,0:01:15.18,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Only one, my life
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.18,0:01:18.47,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,不久后人生即将画上句号
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.47,0:01:21.56,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,仅有空虚又怎够将我填饱？
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.56,0:01:22.69,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Dancing dancing
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.69,0:01:24.27,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Morning morning
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.27,0:01:29.65,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,立足原点  保持新鲜
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.65,0:01:32.82,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,做我所愿
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.82,0:01:35.62,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Every night, every time
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.62,0:01:42.54,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,活至尽兴  玩到疲倦
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.13,0:01:46.71,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Dystopia to song of the dead!!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.00,0:01:49.51,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Dystopia to song of the dead!!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.88,0:01:52.34,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,Dystopia to song of the dead!!
